{"tid":2342064,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"今日有冇人一齊行山10","createTime":"2020-12-26T22:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T02:21:44.000Z","uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a75fc426e031deab7fca12f7b4651d23c93e168a","tid":2342064,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T22:12:19.000Z","msg":"全身酸到醒咗<br />\n星期五水泉澳行到飛鵝山再落觀塘<br />\n之後再去油塘打羽毛球<br />\n星期六紅梅谷行筆架山去大埔道落深水埗<br />\n呢個聖誕都算好充實<br />\n十月頭開始行山都就三個月<br />\n好開心自己可以堅持落去<br />\n一齊行山post之前好多膠post<br />\n亦感激各位巴絲打鼓勵<br />\n多謝琴日陪我行山十位高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日仲諗緊行邊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者你地睇下有冇人撞岩路線係到討論"},{"pid":"a49bd8b119fccdd5f2febb82d4dd50262528b372","tid":2342064,"uid":312363,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T00:01:39.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af6e92f4345588e11b83b2b90a2b274186cfa0a","tid":2342064,"uid":358542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T00:09:28.000Z","msg":"有冇行過大東北？"},{"pid":"0f6ca24378b36da3596ebb9e1a0f561f01491480","tid":2342064,"uid":236505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T00:37:04.000Z","msg":"希望毒巴減肥搵到女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2c2d957bbd8fada8b92f89136492954075d573","tid":2342064,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a49bd8b119fccdd5f2febb82d4dd50262528b372","tid":2342064,"uid":312363,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T00:01:39.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T02:03:51.000Z","msg":"多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6b96cd4c05def71d1261e005ab070695bde946","tid":2342064,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1af6